Ugh, it's hot.

115
00:09:20,033 --> 00:09:23,200
 He won't eat meat that's boiled in water, so give him seafood porridge. 

116
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:26,467
He doesn't eat meat that's boiled in water?

117
00:09:26,467 --> 00:09:28,933
That's unusual.

118
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,967
Still, since I'm doing this, I'll make it myself with care

119
00:09:31,967 --> 00:09:36,667
