 A minute later, when he got on again, the inside of his jumper had slimmed down. 

168
00:13:18,233 --> 00:13:20,533
 Right? 

169
00:13:20,533 --> 00:13:23,100
Hey, I'm pretty good, almost like a detective. Right?

170
