00:20:15,933 --> 00:20:19,567
I talked on the phone earlier with her.

260
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:31,600
Hello?

261
00:20:31,600 --> 00:20:33,533
Sis?

262
00:20:36,700 --> 00:20:38,533
